io.requery.query

Class FieldExpression<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.requery.query.FieldExpression<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - field type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aliasable<Expression<V>>, Conditional<Condition<V>,V>, Expression<V>, Functional<V>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AliasedExpression, AttributeBuilder, Function, NamedExpression

    public abstract class FieldExpression<V>
extends Object
implements Aliasable<Expression<V>>, Functional<V>, Conditional<Condition<V>,V>, Expression<V>
    Represents a field expression for which functions, aliasing etc can be applied.
